Student Management System

-> This is a full-stack web application built using Spring Boot (backend) and Angular (frontend) 
to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on student details.

-> Add new student details

-> View all students

-> Update student information

-> Delete a student record

Backend (Spring Boot)

-> Spring Boot

-> Spring Data JPA

-> MySQL Database

-> REST API

Frontend (Angular)

-> Angular

-> TypeScript

-> Bootstrap 

Setup Instructions

Backend Setup

1. Open the backend folder in your IDE (like IntelliJ or Eclipse).
2. Configure MySQL database in application.properties.
3. Run the Spring Boot application.

Frontend Setup

1. Navigate to the frontend folder.
2. Install dependencies.
3. Run the Angular application.
4. Open http://localhost:4200 in the browser.


